column5: Nathan delivers a wide range of gear to compliment your everyday running essentials including hats, bandanas, beanies, socks, run laces, and dog harnesses and leashes – with the same attention to detail in fabrics, reflectivity and storage. Additionally, our line of run fresh and sports detergent products is designed to outsmart the odors and keep your performance gear like new. Whether your shoes, gym bags or garments are smelling a little too funky, we’ve got your covered with odor eliminators and revitalizing cleaners in a variety of applications from liquid to capsules to wipes.

column23: Looking for the best sports training gear? Check out the market leader in creating ground-breaking running equipment and accessories.  From Running Socks, Hats, Apparel & Detergent.
column39: Not just your everyday hat, Nathan headwear adds purpose to style with thoughtful storage, cool comfort and reflectivity. Depending on your need, Nathan hats, beanies, bandanas and gaiters are purpose-built to overcome a variety of challenges, from heat to darkness to on-the-go storage. Our headwear features a variety of on-trend styles and designs.
column42: Take your best furry friend along for the run with ease, comfort and less resistance with our K9 essentials. Inspired by tried-and-true Nathan race vests, the leash, harness and runners belt feature quality, comfortable material with reflective detail for enhanced visibility. Plus the attachment points are in just the right place to minimize pulling and encourage your dog to run alongside you.
column43: The perfect balance of fun, fit and function, Nathan running sock are playful, and perform to boot. Designed to optimize support, comfort and performance, our socks feature a blend of merino guaranteed to keep your feet happy with anti-blister and breathable yarns. Our socks feature limited edition designs so be sure to grab a pair of each for the ultimate collection.
column44: Safety is one of our core features across all our running products. The Nathan face mask delivers an exclusive design to provide uninterrupted activity while keeping you and others safe.  Intended for all athletes and sports, it’s the only athlete-driven face mask designed to keep you both moving and safe. Our exclusive Quick-flip design allows for quick, unobstructed access to hydration without removing the mask or touching your face. It is lightweight, layered and breathable with moisture control to wick away sweat while keeping you cool and dry. The low-profile, secure fit helps you play safe without compromise or restricting your athletic performance. It’s a perfect face mask for athletes at all levels.
column45: Power Wash is a sports laundry detergent built for a runner's life. Better for your clothes AND the planet, our detergent tackles the toughest stains and odors while revitalizing and restoring your favorite gear. It also works hard to preserve technical performance fabrics wash after wash. Available in liquid, capsules and wipes, Power Wash should be a part of every runner's routine.

column5: Nathan is the trusted leader in running hydration, offering vests, bottles, flasks, waist packs, and handhelds built to keep runners performing at their best. Designed with superior form, fit, and function, our gear ensures you stay hydrated and comfortable on every run.

column23: Sports hydration and running gear designed to help you run stronger and longer! Find waist packs, bottles, flasks, and more. Check out our wide selection! Shop now and earn Free Shipping with Qualifying Orders!
column60: Nathan is the industry leader in hydration solutions for runners and has been making hydration vests and packs for over 30 years. We lead by creating hydration solutions that fit better, run better, and simply perform better. Every Nathan hydration vest and pack is designed to be lightweight and comfortable with easy access to hydration and storage. All of our hydration vests and packs are durable, feature adjustable side straps for a perfect fit, soft perimeter binding to prevent chafing and smart pockets for easy access to essentials.
column61: Proper hydration is the number one need for any runner, and Nathan’s expertise in this category can be seen in any one of our hydration solutions. Waist belts make the perfect pack for walkers, joggers and runners, allowing for quick and easy access to hydration and essentials. Our waist belts are comfortable, lightweight and adjustable with an ergo-shaped, bounce-free design. Hydration is always easy, and bottles can be accessed effortlessly with our intuitive designs. Smart storage is included with thoughtful zippered pockets and a stash pouch for smaller items.
column62: Handhelds are our bestselling product and there’s a good reason for it. As the industry leader in hydration solutions, Nathan is always one step ahead in handheld hydration. We offer two primary types of handhelds – Hard Flasks and Soft Flasks. Both feature our patented grip-free design that keeps hydration in reach and always at the ready while maintaining a relaxed hand when running. We also offer a variety of solutions for carrying extra gear, a phone, your keys, or other small items like energy gels. All flasks are available in both insulated and non-insulated versions.

column5: We know that running presents challenges day and night and a runner's safety is of paramount importance. Nathan offers a comprehensive line of products designed to empower runners to put in the miles and, most importantly, get home safely. We pioneered safety features like reflectivity and wearable lights, adding comfort, fit and intuitive design to the category. Our extensive collection of safety gear includes head lamps, flashlights, reflective accessories, face masks and wearable lights. Now, we continue to push the significance of safety even further with our SaferRun collection of personal alarms. See, be seen and be heard with confidence with Nathan safety gear.

Running Safety & Visibility Gear

We know that running presents challenges day and night and a runner's safety is of paramount importance. Nathan offers a comprehensive line of products designed to empower runners to put in the miles and, most importantly, get home safely. We pioneered safety features like reflectivity and wearable lights, adding comfort, fit and intuitive design to the category. Our extensive collection of safety gear includes head lamps, flashlights, reflective accessories, face masks and wearable lights. Now, we continue to push the significance of safety even further with our SaferRun collection of personal alarms. See, be seen and be heard with confidence with Nathan safety gear.


Shop Running Safety Gear & Accessories: Alarms | Headlamps | Flashlights | Wearable Lights | Reflective Visibility Gear

column79: Be safe. Be seen. Be heard. The Nathan SaferRun personal alarm series provides you with more confidence while running. With these portable alarms, you can quickly and effectively let people know you are there and if something is wrong while running. The devices feature a universal clip that allows the alarm to be securely attached to any gear or clothing, helping to boost your safety while on the road. The sirens featured in the SaferRun series are activated with a one-handed quick pull cord and produce an alarm so loud, it can be heard over from over 600 ft away. Best of all it cannot be used against you.

column5: We know a thing or two about making hydration products and our water bottles are one of our top sellers. Our bottles feature a smaller narrow spout in addition to a large wide mouth. All of our bottles are BPA-free and are loaded with odorless and tasteless technology so you can have a sip of fresh whatever every time. Our bottles come in 750ml, 1L, or 1.5L so you can choose the perfect bottle for you. Soft flasks are perfect for packing into your hydration packs in the front pockets or the back storage or stash pocket. Pick from a standard soft flask bottle or an insulated one that helps keep your fluids cooler 38% longer. Don't hesitate and find out why our bottles are some of the best in the industry.

column5: Going on a run or jog and don't want to carry a hydration pack or belt? Our handheld bottles and flasks are the perfect solutions to keep your hydration liquid close by without getting your hand tired. There are plenty of options available to you when it comes to choosing the perfect handheld. Some options include storage pockets for keys, phones, and other small items. Also available are double-walled insulated handheld bottles to keep your liquid at a steady temperature for long periods of time. Our sizes range from 12oz for your short runs to a larger 20oz handheld for longer runs or trails. Stay hydrated with comfort and shop for the perfect handheld water bottle for your lifestyle.

column5: Using a hydration belt is essential when you need to stay light while needing to take some of your essentials and a place to store your water or hydration liquid. One important aspect of a hydration belt is the ability to store water bottles on it with quick access to avoid stopping during your run. Take your keys, phone, wireless earphones case, or other similarly sized items to store in the pocket of the belt. If you're looking for a more compact belt, you can check out our running waist belts that are perfect for short runs and holding small items like your keys.
